 kg\", \"from\": 1107, \"to\": 1113}, {\"ngram\": \"the qualifying tournament\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1174}, {\"ngram\": \"an underdog\", \"from\": 1178, \"to\": 1189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he took down opponents from Saudi Arabia, the UAE, and Afghanistan in a fashion that belied his young age.\", \"from\": 1206, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1244, \"end\": 1250, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7946467476756426e-13, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 1256, \"end\": 1259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates\", \"score\": 0.9943832193549647, \"rank\": 0.005648507070401945, \"text\": \"UAE\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Arab_Emirates\"}, {\"begin\": 1265, \"end\": 1276, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"score\": 0.9999982664727687, \"rank\": 1.733527043696464e-06, \"text\": \"Afghanistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Afghanistan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"opponents\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"a fashion\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1289}, {\"ngram\": \"his young age\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One would never know-unless they were looking at his baby-faced visage-that as recently as two years ago, Ismail was competing solely in youth competitions.\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1423, \"end\": 1429, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isma'il_Pasha\", \"score\": 0.9995147062426551, \"rank\": 0.00047323440652605203, \"text\": \"Ismail\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isma'il_Pasha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Isma'il_Pasha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One\", \"from\": 1317, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"his baby-faced visage\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"youth competitions\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1472}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Posting on his Instagram after achieving entry, Ismailwrote,\\\"Very proud and happy to say that I have made it this far.\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1489, \"end\": 1498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.621548764642272e-19, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"entry\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1520}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All thanks to my amazing coach and the Palestinian federation for being the best support system anyone can have.\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1632, \"end\": 1643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"score\": 0.9994640523420867, \"rank\": 0.0005079619872619227, \"text\": \"Palestinian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Palestinians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All thanks\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1603}, {\"ngram\": \"my amazing coach\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1623}, {\"ngram\": \"the best support system\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1688}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1695}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A chance of a lifetime indeed; and now one step closer to an Olympic medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A chance\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1714}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 1718, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic medal\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1780}]}, {\"senten